@node "noo" "What will it not do?"

  DMS2HD can only decrunch Amiga DOS archives to Harddisk.
  Don`t try it with NDOS disks! It won`t work...

@endnode
 
@node "how" "How does DMS2HD work?"

  The idea of DMS2HD is simple. DMS2HD executes the following
  steps:

  1. It creates a RAD: disk in FastRAM.
  2. It decrunches the DMS archive to this RAD:
  3. It copies the contents from RAD to the harddisk
  4. It formats the RAD:
  5. ...and destroys it after a reboot

  That`s the whole mystery :)

@endnode

