@node "wasmacht" "Introduction"

  DMS2HD is a more or less powerful program which can decrunch
  your .DMS archives *DIRECT* to HD/RAM. Decrunching a DMS
  disk is now very fast (5 secs).

  DMS2HD is a CLI/WB program. You can easily use it in conjunction
  with a directory manager like DirOpus, but you can also double-
  click the icon and use the marvellous MUI GUI.

  DMS2HD can use the executable DMS or the xadmaster.library by
  Dirk St÷cker for decrunching.

  Decrunching a DMS archive is simple.
  See how @{"easy" link "ques"} it is.
@endnode

